Mobile Battery Life Optimization Module

This module provides comprehensive battery life optimization for mobile applications.
Implements power consumption analysis, energy-efficient algorithms, background task optimization,
and battery-aware features with device-specific power management strategies.

Key Features:
- Power consumption monitoring and analysis
- Energy-efficient algorithm implementation
- Background task power optimization
- Screen brightness and display optimization
- Network activity battery impact reduction
- CPU and GPU power management
- Location services optimization
- Sensor usage optimization
- Push notification efficiency
- Battery-aware feature degradation
- Charging state detection and adaptation
- Thermal management integration
- Power usage analytics and reporting
- Cross-device battery optimization
- Real-time power consumption feedback

Provides complete battery optimization system for building mobile applications
with extended battery life and intelligent power management.
:End Note

